{"tid":1550654,"cid":31,"subCid":9,"title":"設計旗幟的五個基本原則","createTime":"2019-09-07T16:59:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-20T18:30:28.000Z","uid":312333,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"5de0a8b4e1945a53de688c68a9568cc2421521b5","tid":1550654,"uid":312333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:59:01.000Z","msg":"根據北美旗幟學協會旗幟學家泰德&middot;凱伊對旗幟的研究<br />\n<br />\n第一，設計要簡單。 旗幟應該設計簡單， 連小孩子也能記住畫出來。<br />\n第二，使用有意義的象徵。<br />\n第三， 使用兩到三種基本顏色。<br />\n第四， 不要有字母或者印章。 絕對不要使用任何字體。<br />\n第五， 要獨特。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ted.com/talks/roman_mars_why_city_flags_may_be_the_worst_designed_thing_you_ve_never_noticed/transcript?language=zh-tw&amp;fbclid=IwAR0KGai6nSq7ojV84IsvuVgb2HOK7CnLJzmMrWUTavoqieeu5n4rUk3MX48#t-528776\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ted.com%2Ftalks%2Froman_mars_why_city_flags_may_be_the_worst_designed_thing_you_ve_never_noticed%2Ftranscript%3Flanguage%3Dzh-tw%26fbclid%3DIwAR0KGai6nSq7ojV84IsvuVgb2HOK7CnLJzmMrWUTavoqieeu5n4rUk3MX48%23t-528776&d=2M92vpXgCVs0KpVIJKRQCy%2F0jIrp0bHqVoz25JuQVd4%3D&h=634f0a48\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ted.com/talks/roman_mars_why_city_flags_may_be_the_worst_designed_thing_you_ve_never_noticed/transcript?language=zh-tw&amp;fbclid=IwAR0KGai6nSq7ojV84IsvuVgb2HOK7CnLJzmMrWUTavoqieeu5n4rUk3MX48#t-528776</a>"},{"pid":"3267f4637de1daf9186dc9685b151a37f2af6e3b","tid":1550654,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:00:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5fdf7d9cc37c9c9f02f0f0fcda99503e3dd46000","tid":1550654,"uid":312333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:19:00.000Z","msg":"P牌一推"},{"pid":"64aaf5edf32b9834973e3ad8d41d67feb75bc6ae","tid":1550654,"uid":59832,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:29:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VHC7njB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVHC7njB.png&h=3b13bfdd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"210974fb359a2c44f096b0b9d22fea12397250fb","tid":1550654,"uid":257422,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:30:59.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我警告你班仆街！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">聽日啲<span style=\"color: red;\">美國</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">國旗</span>唔好周圍掉！<br />\n路邊見到唔該即刻幫手執返！<br />\n完咗活動攞返屋企收藏！</span></span><br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/evxvjtB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FevxvjtB.jpg&h=73325a8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"> 快啲聽熟加背歌詞，<br />\n唱得莊嚴啲！</span>\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/PWMy7Rpk5Bo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPWMy7Rpk5Bo&d=2M92vpXgCVs0KpVIJKRQCy%2F0jIrp0bHqVoz25JuQVd4%3D&h=460947d5\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/PWMy7Rpk5Bo</a><br />\n</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n分段背易啲背：<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Oh, say can you see,</span></span><br />\nBy the dawn's early light,<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">What so proudly we hailed,</span><br />\nAt the twilight's last gleaming?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Whose broad stripes and bright stars,</span><br />\nThrough the perilous fight,<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">O'er the ramparts we watched,</span><br />\nWere so gallantly streaming.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">And the rocket's red glare,</span><br />\nThe bombs bursting in air,<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Gave proof through the night,</span><br />\nThat our flag was still there.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Oh say does that star spangled banner yet wave,</span><br />\n<br />\nFor the land of the free, and the home of the brave.</div><br />\n<br />\n聽日見！</span>"},{"pid":"bca04d51ebc8022d3b1ea4ff32482b8d2b5e0ce0","tid":1550654,"uid":149212,"like":13,"dislike":8,"score":5,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:34:05.000Z","msg":"612已經有post講過<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m6hZyyP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm6hZyyP.png&h=03adc60a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢種設計幾靚"},{"pid":"c30de931e8b97ca6330f3e011c7d3ad65fe14995","tid":1550654,"uid":159997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"64aaf5edf32b9834973e3ad8d41d67feb75bc6ae","tid":1550654,"uid":59832,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:29:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VHC7njB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVHC7njB.png&h=3b13bfdd&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:35:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"448a6aee7